      "description": "Wan 2.2 14B image-to-video in GGUF Q4_K_M — lighter on VRAM than the fp8 build, tuned for 12 GB cards. 4-step dual-expert (high steps 0-2, low steps 2-4) with the lightx2v distill LoRAs. Animate a still image with a motion prompt.",
