        "requirements": {
          "minVramGB": 8,
          "recommendedVramGB": 12,
          "minRamGB": 32,
          "sizeGB": 20,
          "notes": "Wan 2.2 14B I2V GGUF Q4_K_M (2 experts ~9 GB each, diffusion_models via UnetLoaderGGUF) + umt5 encoder (clip\\) + Wan 2.1 VAE + the wan2.2 i2v lightx2v 4-step LoRAs (high+low). 4-step dual-expert split (high 0-2, low 2-4), euler/simple, cfg 1. GGUF is lighter than the built-in fp8 Wan 2.2 I2V (min 16 GB) - runs 480p on ~8 GB, 720p needs ~16 GB (14B model); 12 GB cards should use 480p + short clips. Needs KJNodes + RES4LYF extensions (bundled in engine)."
